item.description:
What you resist, persists. Overcome procrastination 
today. Feel good about yourself! 

Stop procrastination in its tracks and transform it into Inspired Action.

Learn several simple techniques that allow you to
conquer your avoidance behavior, easily organize
your life, find more energy, and accomplish more
than you could ever dream possible.

Wear warm comfortable clothing and bring a pillow, mat, and blanket, if desired.

 

For more information, visit: http://www.hypnosis.ws

 

Preregistration enrollment must be completed through Women of Wisdom at least 3 days in advance. Men are welcome.

For more info, visit: http://www.localendar.com/public/km
